# GoLic ignore file — https://github.com/Bugs5382/golic
# Ignore everything...
*

# ...but inject the Apache-2.0 header into these source types:
!*.yaml
!*.yml
!*.sh
!*.tpl
!Dockerfile

# ...even when they live in subdirectories:
!*/

# Never: the license texts, Markdown (no header), vendored subcharts,
# the docs site, dependencies, build output, and scratch:
/LICENSE
/NOTICE
**/*.md
/charts/**
**/charts/**
/website/**
/node_modules/**
**/node_modules/**
/docs/**
/.superpowers/**
